<FlowDocument PagePadding="5,0,5,0" AllowDrop="True" NumberSubstitution.CultureSource="User" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Verdana" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">Watermark Text</Run></Paragraph><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">If you like to add text as watermark to your images, please enter your desired text here. If nothing is entered, the program will ignore the task to add text watermark.</Run></Paragraph><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">If you need to break your text into multiple lines, simply press "Enter" at where you need a new line, the text box will automatically expand to fit your text.</Run></Paragraph><Paragraph><Run FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="13.3333333333333" xml:lang="en-ca">Here you also can insert your selected Exif macros from photos (JPG files only) into your watermark text. For example you want to include date or time when the photo was taken to watermark text, you can simply select "Date Taken" from Exif toolbar.</Run></Paragraph></FlowDocument>